## Key Patterns

### Multi-Tenant Isolation
Every table has a `business_id` column and RLS policies that filter by the current user's businesses. See `docs/DATABASE.md` for policy templates.

### Feature Gating
Plan features are gated through `usePlanFeatures()` hook and `<FeatureGate>` component.

### Webhook Handling
All external webhooks (Stripe, Green API) go through signature verification before processing. Provisioning happens webhook-first.

